ZenHouse Media Template Site

Setup:

1. Folder Permissions

    Set 777 to application/cache
    Set 777 to application/uploads and sub-folders

2. Put default data in web_profile, web_settings, contact

3. Setup TinyMCE PDW File Browser

    Change the $uploadpath according to the hosting server setting.

    /pdw_file_browser/config.php

    $uploadpath = '/zhm/application/uploads/assets/';
                  ----------------------------------